29234794[=]ustv[=]Javier[=]2012-04-27 17:54:57[=]用这些俚语装地道吧亲~[=]1. and whatnot =and stuff/and so on……诸如此类的 e.g. They talked about SM and DS and whatnot. = They talked about SM and DS and stuff. 他们聊虐恋啊攻受啊神马的。 2. and then some = and much more than that ……还不止咧 e.g. You were my soulmate and then some. =You were my soulmate and much more than that. 君乃知心，又胜过知心。 （Alanis Morissette《Simple Together》） We fucked and then some. =We fucked and did much more things than fucking. 3.That's an understatement. = The opposite of exaggerating. 言过其实的反义，言不及实。 e.g. A: He's gay. 他是基滴。 B: That's an understatement.= He's WAY gay. 他很基有没有。 Soldier: You're different from any woman I know. Soldier's transexual girl: That's an understatement.= I'm WAY different cuz hello, I'm a chick with a dick. (Showtime电影《Solder's Girl迷恋荷尔蒙》) 4. hotshot 酷人，牛人 A person of impressive skill and daring, especially one who is highly successful and self-assured. e.g. And if I'm hotshot, mom will cut my hair at night. 如果我很酷炫，妈晚上会剪我头发。 (Lady Gaga《Hair》（台译“自由发则”）) 5. Fag hag 腐女（逐词直译：玻璃巫婆） 6. +my ass 屁啊 Brenda (Bourgeois female sex addict who fucks strangers): I fucked them to write my fiction! 我和他们搞是为了小说创作！ Nate (Bren's boyfriend): Fiction my ass! 小说个屁！ （HBO旷世神剧《Six Feet Under生前身后》）
